## Troubleshooting

| Symptom | Fix |
| ------- | --- |
| `No such container: callisto-back-end-postgres-1` | Wrong container name — use `callisto-postgres`, not compose-derived names |
| `ECONNREFUSED` on port 5432 | `docker start callisto-postgres` |
| `Cannot find module 'src/shared/...'` during migration | Add `-r tsconfig-paths/register` (command above) |
| RabbitMQ connection warnings | Start `callisto-rabbitmq`, wait, restart API |
| API up but Atlas cannot reach Callisto | Confirm `# CALLISTO_API_URL` is commented for local; align Callisto `APP_PORT` with Quasar proxy default (`3003`) or set an explicit localhost URL |
| S3/SQS errors on file ops | Refresh AWS credentials from Planet Portal |

